Shopify Product & Order Import
Local Setup Guide  —  NextGen OMS + Maarg
Prerequisites  
Go to NextGen-OMS -> Hamburger Menu -> under the shopify section -> shopify shop.  
Have your Shopify Access Token, Client Secret, and Shop ID ready before starting.
https://nextgen-oms.hotwax.io/

Step 1: Create the Shopify Shop
Log  in to https://ip6-localhost:8443/
Navigate to: Hamburger Menu → Shopify Section → Shopify Shop
Click Create New Shop and fill in:

Field
