Rebuild Search Indexes
Navigate to: https://ip6-localhost:8443/commerce/control/SearchAdmin
Click Refresh All Index
Click Create Product Index — no fields required, just click Create
Click Create Order Index — no fields required, just click Create
Final Verification
Open the Product Page — imported products should be visible
Open the Order Page — imported orders should be visible

Troubleshooting  If nothing appears, check the Maarg terminal logs for ERROR or WARN entries related to the import jobs and trace back to the relevant step above.


